{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"order","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/order","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n<p>order 属性确定被用作<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code></a>元素的矩阵的大小。</p>\n<p>提供的值必须是大于 0 的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Content_type#integer\">&lt;整数&gt;</a>. 第一个值&lt;orderX&gt;,确定矩阵的列数。第二个值&lt;orderY&gt;确定矩阵的行数。如果&lt;orderY&gt;没有指定，那么它的默认值相当于&lt;orderX&gt;的值。</p>\n<p>一个典型的值是 order=\"3\". 建议只使用较小的值 (例如 3); 大值可能会导致较高的 CPU 开销而且通常界面上并不能表现出高耗能造成的效果。</p>\n<p>如果未指定该属性，则其效果就如同指定值为 3.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Usage context","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Categories</th>\n      <th>None</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Value</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Content_type#number-optional-number\">&lt;number-optional-number&gt;</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Animatable</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用 order 属性</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.fxtf.org/filter-effects/#element-attrdef-order","title":"Filter Effects Module Level 2"}],"query":"svg.elements.feConvolveMatrix.order"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Usage context","id":"usage_context"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Elements","id":"elements"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"« SVG At